{"tid":665674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用開廁紙對唔啱位嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2018-05-15T07:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T09:31:24.000Z","uid":65433,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab518d8012c11c9e73d1c9e30e1333a0a983546","tid":665674,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:13:44.000Z","msg":"我成日見啲人話啲廁紙對唔啱位，我真係笑而不語<br />\n不過我見隔籬PO咁多人賴個牌子，我今日就破例教下大家用廁紙<br />\n廁紙係三層(或四層)疊好先CUT位的，基本上<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就算係最差嘅品牌都唔會對唔啱位</span><br />\n對唔啱位係因為你拉錯咗三層裡面的其中一層<br />\n即係例如三層係：<br />\n<br />\nA<br />\nB<br />\nC<br />\n<br />\n你就拉咗<br />\n<br />\nB<br />\nC<br />\nA<br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n<br />\nC<br />\nA<br />\nB<br />\n<br />\n咁梗係唔啱位<br />\n解決方法好簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只要揭多兩層，在任何一個位，搵返啱位嘅ABC出來，由呢格開始掹就得</span><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"830c48ccf9e8f08485ce830841ab2f981a2c7b85","tid":665674,"uid":4780,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:15:38.000Z","msg":"廁紙都要人教點用，家下班00後真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3236b92c9baa985d998e36b55a5469d68b219c57","tid":665674,"uid":57489,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"dfbb56166058357f7d8cc7609c22576e0c783ee3","tid":665674,"uid":65433,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3236b92c9baa985d998e36b55a5469d68b219c57","tid":665674,"uid":57489,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"1999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"哦，你睇唔明牙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets